-2 mb-4 ml-4 list-decimal","children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Deposit a yield-bearing asset (sUSDe, stETH, yvUSDC, etc.)"}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Pendle wraps it into SY (Standardized Yield), then splits into PT + YT"}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"PT (Principal Token):"}]," Redeemable 1:1 for the underlying at maturity. Trades at a discount before maturity — the discount is your fixed yield"]}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"YT (Yield Token):"}]," Receives all variable yield until maturity. If yield goes up, YT is worth more. If yield drops, YT loses value"]}],"\n",["$","li","li-4",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Trade PT or YT on Pendle's AMM to lock in fixed rates or speculate on variable rates"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p","p-3",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Example: If sUSDe yields 10% and you buy PT at a 8% discount, you lock in 8% fixed regardless of what sUSDe yield does. If you buy YT and sUSDe yield spikes to 20%, you profit from the excess."}],"\n",["$","h3","h3-1",{"className":"text-lg font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-3","style":{"fontFamily":"var(--font-montserrat), sans-serif"},"children":"Zirodelta"}],"\n",["$","ol","ol-1",{"className":"space-y-2 mb-4 ml-4 list-decimal","children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":"Deposit $ZDLT as collateral into the vault"}],"\n","$L16","\n","$L17","\n","$L18","\n","$L19","\n"]}],"\n","$L1a","\n","$L1b","\n","$L1c","\n","$L1d","\n","$L1e","\n","$L1f","\n","$L20","\n","$L21","\n","$L22","\n","$L23"